        {
            "title": "美股開市前，美股指期貨集體上升！WTI原油升破116美元後「跳水」，美元短線急跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周二，4月7日，美伊談判「最後期限」逼近，市場屏息以待。美股開市前，美股指期貨集體上升，納指100期貨升0.06%，道指30期貨升逾百點，升幅達0.27%，標普500期貨升0.1%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"190\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aT.nu623eiwVUwTusEGUug--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTE5MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/81662f19e66205ce7193bec6c565056e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">XAU/USD反彈升近1%逼近4700美元大關，白銀接近73美元。原油高位回落，倫敦布倫特原油期貨現報108美元；WTI原油期貨現報112美元，此前一度升破116美元，創52周新高。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"678\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/q0mxRF5RHpULqENyL72TcQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTExNDY-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/d21acbcf49de04bd262b440a08522e8d\" width=\"568\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元指數短線急跌，跌破100整數關口。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6ed99d16-81f0-3588-a747-2477dd682d49-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"578\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wCzu9kT9GLquZRi7Bp8QMg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3OA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/44a4b03098bbbaa4b7a3990fb3daf32b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">比特幣 (BitfinexUSD)跌幅收窄至0.84%，失守7萬美元大關。Coinglass數據顯示，最近24小時，加密貨幣市場超7.5萬人爆倉，爆倉金額達1.63億美元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"579\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UYQO0OkeTvNNH9jm5mX.GA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3OQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/dcd95e66df57cf9944d320ed5514ad1a\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>4</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>月最新</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>精選股嚟咗啦！邊啲個股有入選？依家訂閱</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><str