            "title": "中國股市節後首日，超百股升停！ 滬指收升0.26%，小盤股指升超2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/a6RCAuwenlClVnuZ1wBDBw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEABU081_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com - </strong>周二，4月7日，A股市場全天沖高回落，三大指數集體收升，科創50指數升超1%，微盤股指數升超2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今日市場單邊上行，全市場超3900只個股上升，其中101只個股升停，超1400只個股下跌。滬深兩市成交額1.61萬億，較上一個交易日縮量421億。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至收市，上證綜合指數收升0.26%，報3890.16點，深證成份指數收升0.36%，報13400.41點，創業板綜合指數收升0.36%，報3160.82點，中國A50期貨指數截稿前跌0.6%，報14426點。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-985b6b62-0027-356f-abe9-94808987505c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"580\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oUOPpIrTvjNqn08lYEOJnw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/f1fbb0126a2c38de44f8e591236f2249\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">盤面上，化工板塊持續走強，二十余隻成分股升停，大煉化、有機矽等方向領升，齊翔騰達4天2板，江南高纖、合盛矽業、三房巷升停。PCB概念震盪拉升，同宇新材、巨集昌電子雙雙升停。體育概念反復活躍，金陵體育20cm升停，舒華體育、中體產業、共創草坪升停。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">下跌方面，大金融板塊下挫，保險方向領跌，重慶銀行跌超3%，中國太保跌超2%。創新藥概念多股走弱，聯環藥業觸及跌停，萊美藥業、潤都股份、廣生堂大跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">巨豐投顧郭一鳴指出，清明小長假後的首個交易日，A股走出沖高回落、午後窄幅震盪的行情。當前市場的核心特徵可概括為：修復行情仍在，但反復震盪是必然。如果短期美伊衝突迎來新一輪升級，市場在短期承壓之後，反而可能加速完成「最後一跌」，從而夯實階段性市場底。短期操作上，修復趨勢未變，仍以博弈為主，核心是控制節奏、耐心等待。</p><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>4</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>月最新</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>精選股嚟咗啦！邊啲個股有入選？依家訂閱</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>